Description:
    Concerns are very important to keep thing DRY and reusable and decoupling separate stack from your resources. This generator will help generating concern files faster with templates.

Example:
    rails generate concernize models film concern

    This will create:
        models/concerns/film_concern.rb


    rails generate concernize models film

    This will create:
        models/concerns/film.rb

    rails generate concernize controllers film

    This will create:
        controllers/concerns/film.rb
